# Architecture Taste

- Default: simplest correct implementation. Measure, then optimize. Never optimize at accuracy's expense. Confidence: 0.80
- Agent model config uses string format `"provider/model"`, not object format. Confidence: 0.80
- Chart immutable data = cache forever. Transit = hourly cache. Panchang = daily cache. Confidence: 0.85
- Use `.agents/` prefix for skills and config that must work across multiple harnesses — not harness-specific namespaces. Confidence: 0.85
